{"data":[{"id":"66_1750899500.504","type":"feed","offset":66,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1750899500,"updated_time":1750899500,"target":{"id":"1890750528062984938","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/1890750528062984938","author":{"id":"12e325550bf9e25a2fb45034e3b40b88","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/12e325550bf9e25a2fb45034e3b40b88","user_type":"people","url_token":"quan-wang-zi-yuan-jun","name":"沈清说运营","headline":"咨询dyys57","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c0c46dc0de3ea9dec3d612df3afd8185_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":1,"followers_count":12570,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"created_time":1743570054,"updated_time":1743570054,"voteup_count":2,"thanks_count":0,"comment_count":0,"is_copyable":true,"question":{"id":"367560094","type":"question","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/367560094","author":{"id":"d4d52ca50d71e94ca25fef1b14995f25","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/d4d52ca50d71e94ca25fef1b14995f25","user_type":"people","url_token":"li-ang-41-69-48","name":"你才是臭弟弟","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b63b933eb06924b56b790236cf72a276_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":1,"followers_count":2,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"title":"这个时代什么样的人能够白手起家？","created":1579750373,"answer_count":0,"follower_count":0,"comment_count":0,"bound_topic_ids":[405,1740,12891,108214],"is_following":false,"excerpt":"","relationship":{"is_author":false},"detail":"","question_type":"normal"},"excerpt":"专注到比较变态的人。 我认识的几个白手起家的人，讲的话都不是正常人说的话。 1号：这辈子要么赚个几千万，要么欠个几千万。 2号：这辈子命没了，下辈子还有；钱没赚到，是真不甘心！ 3号：女人只会影响我拔刀的速度，正常有大志向的优秀男青年谁结婚？ ... 这帮人的统一特点就是把事业把赚钱看的比命还重。人生主线，事业为第一要义，其他都得让开为事业服务。专注到这种程度的人，往往会成功！ 其他什么这啊、那啊的特点，往…","excerpt_new":"专注到比较变态的人。 我认识的几个白手起家的人，讲的话都不是正常人说的话。 1号：这辈子要么赚个几千万，要么欠个几千万。 2号：这辈子命没了，下辈子还有；钱没赚到，是真不甘心！ 3号：女人只会影响我拔刀的速度，正常有大志向的优秀男青年谁结婚？ ... 这帮人的统一特点就是把事业把赚钱看的比命还重。人生主线，事业为第一要义，其他都得让开为事业服务。专注到这种程度的人，往往会成功！ 其他什么这啊、那啊的特点，往…","preview_type":"default","preview_text":"","reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp data-pid=\"hhDi5WBu\"\u003e专注到比较变态的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"Li0j9Fvn\"\u003e我认识的几个白手起家的人，讲的话都不是正常人说的话。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"uoycPNKe\"\u003e1号：这辈子要么赚个几千万，要么欠个几千万。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"Jx8sHCbA\"\u003e2号：这辈子命没了，下辈子还有；钱没赚到，是真不甘心！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"geP3osSB\"\u003e3号：女人只会影响我拔刀的速度，正常有大志向的优秀男青年谁结婚？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"N4JSMaUz\"\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"S7NZeNHn\"\u003e这帮人的统一特点就是把事业把赚钱看的比命还重。人生主线，事业为第一要义，其他都得让开为事业服务。专注到这种程度的人，往往会成功！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"X2mEAJPG\"\u003e其他什么这啊、那啊的特点，往往是过度总结。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"APzIVWOX\"\u003e因为人是会随着环境、认知增加而产生不断变化的！比方说今天这个老板对人很豪爽，但是明天因为错信一个朋友，而变得谨慎起来，其实也没什么问题！外人两面都可以评价！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"HLGYnAts\"\u003e所以真正长期驱使他不断前进的——只有对钱的渴望和野心。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"tkbH0f9h\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e对ai和商业感兴趣的欢迎和我交流！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//mp.weixin.qq.com/s/J3FMUxKuyDs7Tuu4GvEYfQ%3Ftoken%3D2129401590%26lang%3Dzh_CN\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0723f11531bc0b1f8cef7c3c2800b61d_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"500\" data-image-height=\"213\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e为什么我要建立一个ai商圈？\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//mp.weixin.qq.com/s/u_NnfqnUj8NH7bnlQMPgdQ%3Ftoken%3D797170152%26lang%3Dzh_CN\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7242c5ecf5d9a44284cd65397aecf9bd_ipico.jpg\" data-image-width=\"0\" data-image-height=\"0\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e为什么我要建立一个企业管理交流群？\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ETkcPiMOIgnbPiiCkM6ZcQ\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2